data.description: Seller offers $3,000 in concessions w/ full price offer! Lovely 2 bedroom/2 bath home in Yuma East 55+. Property boasts added air-conditioned den for entertainment, living space, or crafting. Two tranquil patio areas offer shade & serenity. Easy care landscaping all around, & beautifully raised garden bed. Workshop with benches & additional storage. Extended concrete driveway for added parking. Foam insulated roof. Fridge/Washer/Dryer/Microwave to convey! Nearby grocery/dining/healthcare/I-8 access.
